                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-269-18750405 t18750405-269-punishment-32"></join>
                     <hi rend="italic">Seven Years Penal Servitude</hi>
                  </rs>. <hi rend="italic">The prisoner was proved to have been twenty times in custody</hi>.</p>
